## Spacing

Use Tailwind's default spacing scale (4px base). Be consistent.

| Token | Value | Use |
|-------|-------|-----|
| `gap-1` / `p-1` | 4px | Micro spacing — icon padding, badge inline spacing |
| `gap-2` / `p-2` | 8px | Tight spacing — between icon and label, radio options |
| `gap-3` / `p-3` | 12px | Compact — list item padding, inline groups |
| `gap-4` / `p-4` | 16px | Default — card padding, form field gaps |
| `gap-6` / `p-6` | 24px | Comfortable — between form sections, card groups |
| `gap-8` / `p-8` | 32px | Spacious — between page sections |
| `gap-12` / `py-12` | 48px | Section separation on landing pages |
| `gap-16` / `py-16` | 64px | Major page section breaks |

### Rules

- Card internal padding: `p-6` (24px).
- Space between form fields: `space-y-4` (16px) for compact, `space-y-6` (24px) for standard.
- Page section vertical rhythm: `py-12` to `py-16`.
- Max content width: `max-w-4xl mx-auto` for forms and booking flow. `max-w-6xl mx-auto` for landing pages.

