## Components

Use shadcn/ui components for ALL interactive UI. Never build custom versions of primitives.

### Installation

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init  # new-york style, neutral base color, CSS variables enabled
npx shadcn@latest add button input card badge radio-group checkbox select dialog sheet tabs progress toast tooltip calendar form label textarea separator skeleton switch
```

### Component usage patterns

**Button** — `@/components/ui/button`

```tsx
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";

// Variants available: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link
// Sizes available: default, sm, lg, icon

<Button>Primary Action</Button>                    // Filled teal
<Button variant="outline">Secondary</Button>       // Border-only
<Button variant="ghost">Tertiary</Button>           // Text-only
<Button variant="secondary">Muted Action</Button>  // Gray bg
<Button size="lg">Large CTA</Button>                // For hero sections
<Button size="sm">Compact</Button>                  // For inline actions
<Button size="icon"><ArrowRight /></Button>          // Icon-only
```

**Card** — `@/components/ui/card`

```tsx
import { Card, CardContent, CardDescription, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "@/components/ui/card";

<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Clinic Name</CardTitle>
    <CardDescription>North York, ON · 5 km</CardDescription>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    {/* Clinic details */}
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

**Input** — `@/components/ui/input`

```tsx
import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input";
import { Label } from "@/components/ui/label";

<div className="space-y-2">
  <Label htmlFor="email">Email</Label>
  <Input id="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" />
</div>
```

**RadioGroup** — `@/components/ui/radio-group`

```tsx
import { RadioGroup, RadioGroupItem } from "@/components/ui/radio-group";

<RadioGroup defaultValue="yes">
  <div className="flex items-center space-x-2">
    <RadioGroupItem value="yes" id="yes" />
    <Label htmlFor="yes">Yes, I have a requisition</Label>
  </div>
  <div className="flex items-center space-x-2">
    <RadioGroupItem value="no" id="no" />
    <Label htmlFor="no">No, I don't have one yet</Label>
  </div>
</RadioGroup>
```

**Badge** — `@/components/ui/badge`

```tsx
import { Badge } from "@/components/ui/badge";

// Variants: default, secondary, destructive, outline
<Badge>MRI</Badge>
<Badge variant="secondary">Full Body Scan Only</Badge>
<Badge variant="outline">No border crossing</Badge>
```

**Dialog (Modal)** — `@/components/ui/dialog`
- Max width: `sm:max-w-[480px]` on desktop.
- Always include a close button and keyboard dismiss (Escape).

**Toast** — `@/components/ui/toast`
- Use for non-blocking confirmations and errors.
- Success: default variant. Error: destructive variant.

**Progress** — `@/components/ui/progress`
- Use for the booking flow step indicator.

### Rules

- Never create a custom button, input, select, radio, checkbox, modal, or toast. Use shadcn/ui.
- Import from `@/components/ui/*` only.
- Import icons from `lucide-react` only. Never inline SVGs.
- Use the `cn()` utility from `@/lib/utils` to conditionally merge classes.
- All form validation uses `react-hook-form` + `zod` schemas.

