## Do / Don't

| ✅ Do | ❌ Don't |
|-------|---------|
| Use `bg-background`, `text-foreground` | Use `bg-white`, `text-black`, raw hex values |
| Use `<Button>` from shadcn/ui | Create a custom `<button>` with inline styles |
| Use `text-sm font-medium` for labels | Use arbitrary font sizes like `text-[13px]` |
| Use `space-y-4` for form field gaps | Eyeball spacing with random padding values |
| Use `cn()` for conditional classes | String concatenate classNames manually |
| Use `lucide-react` icons | Inline `<svg>` or import from random icon packs |
| Use `font-mono` for prices and data | Use sans-serif for numerical data |
| Build mobile-first, then add breakpoints | Build desktop-first and try to shrink it |
| Use `Skeleton` components for loading | Show blank space or spinners in content areas |
| Use `Toast` for confirmations | Use `alert()` or inline success messages |
